import React from 'react'
import { Container, Form, InputGroup } from 'react-bootstrap'


const NavBar = () => {
  return (
    <Container>
        <Form>
            <Container>
                <Form.Group>
                    <InputGroup></InputGroup>
                </Form.Group>
            </Container>
        </Form>
    </Container>
  )
}

export default NavBar
